# Copy to .env for local runs. Never commit the real .env (it's gitignored).
#
# Note: this package has NO AiOps Enabler reporting code and reads no
# AiOps-related env vars -- that integration lives entirely in
# .github/workflows/scheduled.yml as a copyable template. See README
# "Optional: AiOps Enabler integration".

# Optional: JSON array overriding the default target list (latest
# GitHub release of each of the other four agents in this project).
# Each item: {"name", "kind" ("github_release"|"url"|"file"), "location",
# "freshness_hours" (optional, defaults to 720 = 30 days)}.
BACKUP_AUDIT_TARGETS=
